race.comment: BORN SURVIVOR (1) was prominent from the outset and fought on for third over 1400m at Wangaratta. Missed by a similar margin at Bairnsdale prior and will get every chance from a low gate with Brad Rawiller staying aboard. DEEP STREAM (2) has been racing over further and was tracking well before the latest. Drops back to the mile but just missed here when last tried at the trip. JAPPALOUIS (4) has been mixing trips and was plainer in his last two. Maps best and on his best form is one of the key runners. SI SI SIR (6) debuts with the blinkers on and has had a stack of jumpouts. Keep a close eye on the betting moves. MEKA VIBE (5) wasn't far away at Corowa and has a key jockey switch to McDougall. Will be fitter and should be around the mark.
